          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Foils of thorium, 30 mg/cm**2 thick, containing 99.9%",
                " of Th-232."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "PART-DET": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "FF"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "PLATE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Two  8  micron  thick strips of polycarbonate",
                " films (KIMFOL) with thorium sample between them."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The photofission  cross  section  sig(g,f)  at photon",
                " energy Eg is related to the fission fragments counts",
                " in a strip."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The  errors  are  given  include  counting",
                " errors,  errors  in  efficiency  calibration  of the",
                " g-ray and fission fragment detectors,  uncertainties",
                " in the angular distribution of the fission fragments",
                " and g-rays,  and uncertainties in the  alignment  of",
                " the  thorium  foils and kimfol films relative to the",
                " proton target."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The cross   sections   given   were   corrected   for",
                " contributions  caused  by  the  unwanted  gamma-rays",
                " emitted  from some (p,g) resonances.  Except for one",
                " case,  these corrections did not exceed 10%  of  the",
                " presented  values.  The  sum of the corrections from",
                " fission caused by neutrons from (g,n),  (g,2n),  and",
                " fission,  as well as contribution from (g,nf),  were",
                " estimated to be smoller than 2%."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The photofission cross section of Th-232 was measured",
                " in the 5.8 - 12.0 MeV energy range with  an  average",
                " photon  energy  resolution  of 600 eV.  Intermediate",
                " structure was observed at 5.91, 5.97, and 6.31 MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
